00:39:45.553 --> 00:39:47.221
Don't you think that's weird?

506
00:39:47.355 --> 00:39:49.790
-People grieve in different--
-Get away from me!

507
00:40:10.544 --> 00:40:11.846
Will's dead.

508
00:40:11.979 --> 00:40:14.015
And now you inflict this on us?

509
00:40:15.249 --> 00:40:16.784
That's enough.

510
00:40:16.918 --> 00:40:20.688
-Dad. You don't look good--
-It's your fault he's dead.

511
00:40:20.821 --> 00:40:22.823
You didn't stop him
getting to the car!

512
00:40:22.957 --> 00:40:24.525
