I had nothing to do with it.

513
00:40:24.659 --> 00:40:25.826
Will got into a fight
with Alice. and he--

514
00:40:25.960 --> 00:40:28.362
What? Are you implying
it was my fault?

515
00:40:28.495 --> 00:40:29.964
-No. no. of course not.
-You were there.

516
00:40:30.097 --> 00:40:31.498
You couldn't stop him from
getting in the car either.

517
00:40:31.632 --> 00:40:32.733
I know. Alice.
I know. I tried.

518
00:40:32.867 --> 00:40:34.402
We tried.
Okay. I didn't.

519
00:40:34.535 --> 00:40:36.003
-Doesn't mean it's my fault.
-That's not what I'm saying.

520
00:40:36.137 --> 00:40:37.371
-It's exactly what you said.
-Alice. no.

521
00:40:37.505 --> 00:40:38.873
- Alice. I think--
- No.

522
00:40:39.006 --> 00:40:40.007
I think you should all
mind your own business.

523
00:40:40.141 --> 00:40:40.508
You don't know anything.

524
00:40:41.509 --> 00:40:43.110
You're glad he's dead.

525
00:40:43.244 --> 00:40:46.213
Please. please. please. Will's
looking down on us from above.

526
00:40:47.982 --> 00:40:49.016
From above?

527
00:40:53.354 --> 00:40:55.923
He's down below.

528
00:41:01.195 --> 00:41:03.364
