Stop it right now!

529
00:41:03.496 --> 00:41:04.665
- Stop!
- No!

530
00:41:08.102 --> 00:41:09.503
The dog!

531
00:41:10.104 --> 00:41:11.105
Help me.

532
00:41:12.173 --> 00:41:13.207
Help me.

533
00:41:13.341 --> 00:41:14.308
Help me!

534
00:41:14.442 --> 00:41:16.377
-Get your keys.
-Okay.

535
00:41:16.510 --> 00:41:17.778
Take him to the hospital.

536
00:41:18.946 --> 00:41:20.915
Thya! I need help.
Grab his arm.

537
00:41:21.048 --> 00:41:22.783
- I got him. I got him.
- Be careful.

538
00:41:22.917 --> 00:41:25.119
What did we do to deserve this?

539
00:41:26.921 --> 00:41:29.623
