saying goodbye.

540
00:41:34.996 --> 00:41:36.998
Jesus fucking Christ.
is he fucking crazy?

541
00:41:37.131 --> 00:41:38.466
Thya. please. Give me a second.

542
00:41:38.599 --> 00:41:40.801
-He killed your fucking dog!
-I know!

543
00:41:42.203 --> 00:41:45.206
Shit. shit. He's fucking
bleeding everywhere. Shit.

544
00:41:46.874 --> 00:41:49.543
Shit. shit. Come on!

545
00:41:53.948 --> 00:41:55.383
-Joe?
-What?

546
00:41:55.516 --> 00:41:56.784
Your dad.

547
00:42:11.098 --> 00:42:12.566
No! No!

548
00:42:53.274 --> 00:42:54.175
Oh. my fucking God!

549
00:43:11.292 --> 00:43:12.593
Stop!

550
00:43:14.862 --> 00:43:16.063
Let her go!

551
00:43:17.331 --> 00:43:19.400
I said let her go!

552
00:43:19.534 --> 00:43:20.535
Fucking shoot him!

553
00:43:22.403 --> 00:43:24.905
Fucking shoot him! Joe!

554
00:43:27.542 --> 00:43:29.810
Shoot me. Joe.

555
00:43:31.045 --> 00:43:32.379
Shoot me.

556
00:43:33.314 --> 00:43:35.182
Shoot me.

557
00:43:35.316 --> 00:43:36.317
Shoot me. Joe!

558
00:43:36.450 --> 00:43:37.451
Shoot me!

559
00:44:00.609 --> 00:44:02.276
Joseph!

560
00:45:59.360 --> 00:46:00.961
"October. 1983.

561
00:46:01.095 --> 00:46:03.130
That cursed <i>Book of the Dead.</i>

562
00:46:03.264 --> 00:46:05.165
I warned them
against reading from it.

563
00:46:05.299 --> 00:46:07.368
The forbidden incantation.

564
00:46:07.501 --> 00:46:10.739
Four words
that can unleash evil.

565
00:46:10.871 --> 00:46:12.973
But they didn't listen.

566
00:46:15.409 --> 00:46:17.111
December. 1983.

567
00:46:17.244 --> 00:46:18.946
At last. I have found it.

568
00:46:19.079 --> 00:46:22.049
A weapon
that can stop them all.

569
00:46:22.182 --> 00:46:27.154
A dagger created
by the Circle of the Wise Men.

570
00:46:27.288 --> 00:46:29.223
<i>The tiniest cut</i>
<i>from this ancient blade</i>

571
00:46:29.356 --> 00:46:31.358
<i>rips their demonic souls</i>
<i>from their bodies.</i>

572
00:46:31.492 --> 00:46:34.228
<i>I've hidden it.</i>
<i>but now must leave again.</i>

573
00:46:34.361 --> 00:46:36.497
<i>These creatures are hunting me</i>

574
00:46:36.631 --> 00:46:40.968
<i>and I must protect</i>
<i>my wife and daughters."</i>

575
00:47:02.524 --> 00:47:03.457
"Kunda."

576
00:47:13.867 --> 00:47:14.803
"Astratta."

577
00:47:26.880 --> 00:47:27.816
"Montosse."

578
00:47:39.493 --> 00:47:40.427
No. fuck this.

579
