586
00:48:56.504 --> 00:48:58.706
She came back for my money.

587
00:50:10.410 --> 00:50:13.413
To your perfect family.

588
00:50:15.817 --> 00:50:17.184
Cheers.

589
00:50:52.352 --> 00:50:53.588
No!

590
00:51:00.528 --> 00:51:02.262
Joe. it hurts.

591
00:51:02.396 --> 00:51:04.599
-Please. Joe.
-Joe. no!

592
00:51:08.168 --> 00:51:09.504
Where is your father?

593
00:51:09.637 --> 00:51:12.239
We gotta go. We gotta go.
Alice! Alice. come on!

594
00:51:13.508 --> 00:51:14.909
