607
00:55:26.127 --> 00:55:26.994
Uh...

608
00:55:28.062 --> 00:55:30.463
Oh. Exactly.

609
00:55:49.584 --> 00:55:53.054
- Oh. my God.
Mom. are you okay?

610
00:55:54.589 --> 00:55:56.023
Mom. are you okay?

611
00:55:58.860 --> 00:56:00.761
You're fine.
