639
01:01:17.444 --> 01:01:20.214
Come here. young lady!
I have what you want!

640
01:01:28.355 --> 01:01:29.690
Be right back. baby.

641
01:01:50.177 --> 01:01:52.079
The money is under my mattress.

642
01:01:53.047 --> 01:01:55.382
Take it and leave us alone.

643
01:01:57.451 --> 01:01:58.319
Aww.

644
01:01:59.521 --> 01:02:01.755
It's all broken in here.

645
01:02:03.424 --> 01:02:05.826
But there is something
that we want

646
01:02:05.960 --> 01:02:08.262
in that little head of yours.

647
01:02:10.998 --> 01:02:13.767
Your husband must have told you
where it is.

648
01:02:18.673 --> 01:02:19.740
Huh?

649
01:02:29.416 --> 01:02:30.284
Mmm.

650
01:02:43.430 --> 01:02:46.000
Boop. This will fix you.

651
01:02:55.209 --> 01:02:56.076
Polly.

652
01:02:57.044 --> 01:02:58.112
where's your leg?

653
01:03:09.890 --> 01:03:11.892
Yeah. They don't--

654
01:03:16.397 --> 01:03:19.933
