662
01:05:05.439 --> 01:05:07.307
Stop hiding stuff
and just tell me.

663
01:05:07.441 --> 01:05:09.410
I saw those fucked up drawings
you threw out.

664
01:05:12.446 --> 01:05:15.182
Did Will ever tell you
about our grandfather?

665
01:05:19.386 --> 01:05:23.257
Growing up. we were always told
he was unstable.

666
01:05:23.390 --> 01:05:25.359
In his journals.
he described it as this group.

667
01:05:25.492 --> 01:05:28.262
Convinced the devil
had been here.

668
01:05:30.063 --> 01:05:33.000
Would return if anyone read
from when he called the...

669
01:05:36.236 --> 01:05:37.471
The <i>Book of the Dead.</i>

670
01:05:46.280 --> 01:05:49.183
My grandfather left his family
to travel the world.

671
01:05:49.316 --> 01:05:52.019
researching
and collecting artifacts

672
01:05:52.152 --> 01:05:54.121
as protection from all this.

673
01:05:54.254 --> 01:05:55.422
You still have them?

674
01:05:57.357 --> 01:06:00.327
My mom asked me to throw
everything away after he died.

675
01:06:00.461 --> 01:06:01.563
-but... No. no. no.
-Fuck.

676
01:06:01.696 --> 01:06:02.797
She asked. but I didn't.

677
01:06:03.865 --> 01:06:06.467
There's still some stuff hidden
up in the attic.

678
01:06:07.468 --> 01:06:08.937
And Thya.

679
