to make sure
there aren't any monsters.

684
01:06:47.842 --> 01:06:48.743
No monsters.

685
01:06:49.443 --> 01:06:50.712
You're lying.

686
01:06:54.716 --> 01:06:56.450
Don't worry.

687
01:06:56.584 --> 01:06:57.652
