that my father stole.

718
01:12:13.868 --> 01:12:16.469
I told you he was a bad man.

719
01:12:17.205 --> 01:12:18.105
It's simple.

720
01:12:18.739 --> 01:12:19.941
Tell them where it is.

721
01:12:20.074 --> 01:12:22.810
Give them what they want.
and this ends.

722
01:12:24.477 --> 01:12:25.780
We can be happy again.

723
01:12:27.181 --> 01:12:28.448
Where... What is...

724
01:12:30.417 --> 01:12:31.552
Our weapon.

725
01:12:34.121 --> 01:12:35.990
We threw everything away.

726
01:12:36.123 --> 01:12:37.024
You're lying to me.

727
01:12:38.659 --> 01:12:39.927
Tell us where it is.

728
01:12:41.562 --> 01:12:42.830
"Us"?

729
01:12:42.964 --> 01:12:44.532
Where is the Kandarian dagger?

730
01:12:53.406 --> 01:12:54.842
Alice...

731
01:12:58.079 --> 01:12:58.980
Leave him alone!

732
01:13:06.654 --> 01:13:09.790
