once we have the dag--

744
01:14:27.401 --> 01:14:28.468
No!

745
01:14:29.570 --> 01:14:30.938
Ah!

746
01:14:31.072 --> 01:14:33.107
- Get off him!
- Mom. Oh!

747
01:14:34.508 --> 01:14:35.776
Get off him!

748
01:14:35.910 --> 01:14:38.813
-Edgar! Get off!
-Oh. fuck.

749
01:14:50.291 --> 01:14:51.726
Stop!

750
01:14:51.859 --> 01:14:54.295
Stop! Stop it! Stop!

751
01:14:56.564 --> 01:14:59.800
