753
01:15:13.514 --> 01:15:15.950
No!

754
01:15:23.624 --> 01:15:24.658
Get off me!

755
01:15:25.192 --> 01:15:26.060
Get off!

756
01:15:33.100 --> 01:15:34.668
No!

757
01:15:35.469 --> 01:15:37.571
No!

758
01:15:38.706 --> 01:15:39.774
