775
01:19:29.403 --> 01:19:30.504
Susan.

776
01:19:30.639 --> 01:19:31.805
Help.

777
01:19:32.641 --> 01:19:33.575
Susan. dear.

778
01:19:34.542 --> 01:19:36.143
would you mind
pushing the throttle

779
01:19:36.277 --> 01:19:39.046
to tear
this bitch's face off. please?

780
01:19:39.179 --> 01:19:41.282
She brought chaos
into this family.

781
01:19:42.049 --> 01:19:44.351
Your son died because of her.

782
01:19:45.953 --> 01:19:47.254
Do it.

783
01:19:47.756 --> 01:19:48.856
For Will.

784
01:19:53.595 --> 01:19:54.495
Do it.

785
01:19:58.265 --> 01:19:59.433
Do it!

786
01:20:03.504 --> 01:20:04.838
Oh. Susan!

787
01:20:05.640 --> 01:20:06.940
Do it.

788
01:20:07.841 --> 01:20:09.276
I'm sorry. Alice.

789
01:21:44.572 --> 01:21:45.607
Is it Joseph?

790
01:21:47.474 --> 01:21:48.475
Is it my son?

791
01:21:56.751 --> 01:21:58.285
No.

792
01:22:29.049 --> 01:22:30.050
What are you doing?

793
01:22:31.619 --> 01:22:32.787
You should be grateful

794
01:22:32.921 --> 01:22:34.154
I didn't leave you back there.

795
01:22:34.689 --> 01:22:36.558
Don't you dare move.

796
01:22:38.959 --> 01:22:40.327
Grateful?

797
01:22:46.200 --> 01:22:48.068
My family is gone.

798
01:22:48.937 --> 01:22:51.205
Everyone I love is gone

799
01:22:51.338 --> 01:22:53.207
because of you.

800
01:22:54.441 --> 01:22:57.444
All you've ever done
is bring us pain.

801
01:23:03.818 --> 01:23:04.886
I hate you.

802
01:23:05.018 --> 01:23:06.888
Oh. shut up. Susan!

803
01:23:07.020 --> 01:23:08.989
Shut the fuck up!

804
01:23:09.122 --> 01:23:11.325
I didn't bring anything
to your family.

805
01:23:11.458 --> 01:23:13.327
It was already there.

806
01:23:14.194 --> 01:23:15.730
You see this?

807
01:23:16.831 --> 01:23:18.131
You see. Susan?

808
01:23:18.265 --> 01:23:19.366
This is your son.

809
01:23:19.500 --> 01:23:21.134
This is what he was capable of.

810
01:23:21.268 --> 01:23:23.638
-It was an accident.
-No. it wasn't!

811
01:23:25.874 --> 01:23:28.510
It was not and you knew.

812
01:23:29.644 --> 01:23:31.345
You knew. Susan.

813
01:23:32.647 --> 01:23:36.049
You deserve everything
that's happened to you.

814
01:23:37.284 --> 01:23:40.555
Every fucking thing.
But you know what?

815
01:23:42.122 --> 01:23:43.423
It's behind me now.

816
01:23:44.224 --> 01:23:46.193
I don't give a shit anymore.

817
01:23:55.837 --> 01:23:56.905
You're right.

818
01:23:57.437 --> 01:24:00.073
Your past is behind you.

819
01:24:01.976 --> 01:24:04.746
Right... Right behind you.

820
01:24:06.280 --> 01:24:08.048
Like a shadow.

821
01:24:09.684 --> 01:24:11.318
Can't escape it.

822
01:24:12.386 --> 01:24:15.122
Just when you think
you're safe.

823
01:24:16.089 --> 01:24:17.157
Healed.

824
01:24:18.225 --> 01:24:21.796
When you breathe
a quivering sigh...

825
01:24:23.463 --> 01:24:26.266
my son will be there.

826
01:24:27.802 --> 01:24:29.503
As a husband should.

827
01:24:31.471 --> 01:24:36.844
And he will burn you down...

828
01:24:37.912 --> 01:24:41.481
like the whore you are.

829
01:24:44.586 --> 01:24:46.888
You will be dead by dawn!

830
01:26:39.000 --> 01:26:40.333
Alice.

831
01:26:40.467 --> 01:26:41.903
Help me up.

832
01:26:42.036 --> 01:26:44.471
I know where the dagger is.
I'll help you find it.

833
01:26:46.641 --> 01:26:48.241
And then
I'll cut you open with it

834
01:26:48.375 --> 01:26:50.044
like my brother should have.

835
01:26:50.945 --> 01:26:53.915
You're worthless.
Just like my grandfather.

836
01:26:54.048 --> 01:26:55.783
Shut up!

837
01:26:55.917 --> 01:26:58.886
He never found it.
and you never will.

838
01:27:00.722 --> 01:27:03.356
Let me end your miserable life.

839
01:27:03.490 --> 01:27:05.993
You like pain. anyway.

840
01:27:09.664 --> 01:27:12.365
That's why you let Will
hurt you. Isn't it?

841
01:27:12.867 --> 01:27:15.770
Poor little Alice.

842
01:27:20.440 --> 01:27:23.644
You'll be found
in an attic alone.

843
01:27:25.245 --> 01:27:27.380
Gutted from tit to tail.

844
01:27:29.382 --> 01:27:31.351
You never wanted kids. anyway.

845
01:27:32.252 --> 01:27:33.554
Your body is useless.

846
01:27:51.271 --> 01:27:52.540
Wrong one.

847
01:27:55.910 --> 01:27:58.746
The Circle of the Wise Men
is dead.

848
01:28:08.355 --> 01:28:09.957
Come here. you little bitch.

849
01:28:10.591 --> 01:28:12.193
I told you it's not here.

850
01:30:24.558 --> 01:30:25.993
My family will...

851
01:30:26.127 --> 01:30:27.061
Fuck your family!

852
01:31:49.777 --> 01:31:51.078
Did you stay

853
01:31:51.212 --> 01:31:52.813
because you liked it?

854
01:31:52.947 --> 01:31:55.549
Or you were too much
of a coward to leave me?

855
01:32:01.122 --> 01:32:02.890
Look at you now.

856
01:32:04.525 --> 01:32:06.894
You still can't leave.

857
01:32:16.670 --> 01:32:19.306
Remember the last thing
you said to me?

858
01:32:23.644 --> 01:32:25.546
"Go to hell."

859
01:32:27.882 --> 01:32:29.717
You got your wish.

860
01:32:42.229 --> 01:32:44.899
I shouldn't have hurt you.
Alice.

861
01:32:45.032 --> 01:32:46.467
I should have killed you.

862
01:33:04.251 --> 01:33:06.954
This is where I promised
I'd always be with you.

863
01:33:26.073 --> 01:33:29.677
Where I promised that not even
death would do us part.

864
01:33:32.046 --> 01:33:35.049
I will keep my promise. Alice.

865
01:33:41.556 --> 01:33:43.023
'Cause without me...

866
01:33:44.859 --> 01:33:46.994
you are nothing.

867
01:34:57.831 --> 01:34:58.899
Hello?

868
01:35:01.468 --> 01:35:02.970
Hello? Hello...

869
01:36:17.211 --> 01:36:21.716
I could never
have lived without you. Alice.

870
01:36:22.483 --> 01:36:24.885
I won't let you live
without me.

871
01:37:03.991 --> 01:37:05.492
Shit.

872
01:37:08.763 --> 01:37:10.264
Where is the dagger?

873
01:37:13.067 --> 01:37:15.436
Where is it?

874
01:37:16.870 --> 01:37:18.339
Where is it. Alice?

875
01:37:21.543 --> 01:37:23.077
Go get it.

876
01:38:41.890 --> 01:38:43.323
Where is the dagger?

877
01:38:43.892 --> 01:38:45.492
Speak or burn. bitch!

878
01:38:46.895 --> 01:38:49.296
Here's your fucking dagger!

879
01:39:11.485 --> 01:39:13.454
I love you.

880
01:39:44.318 --> 01:39:46.286
That is not enough.

881
01:41:20.682 --> 01:41:23.585
<i>...Primary.</i>
<i>five. five. seven. four.</i>

882
01:41:32.292 --> 01:41:33.861
Got a cigarette?

883
01:41:35.563 --> 01:41:38.265
-I'm not really allowed to--
-Just give it to me.

884
01:41:47.542 --> 01:41:48.810
Who did this to you?

885
01:41:56.084 --> 01:41:57.685
My ex-husband.

886
01:44:37.945 --> 01:44:40.648
Wicked little French bitch.

887
01:44:50.825 --> 01:44:53.561
Ma'am! What happened?
Are you okay?

888
01:44:53.694 --> 01:44:57.430
Oh!
Thank Heaven! Please help me!

889
01:44:57.565 --> 01:44:59.567
She stole my legs!

890
01:45:01.202 --> 01:45:03.838
But yours will do just fine.

891
01:48:14.695 --> 01:48:16.130
Yes. sweetie. I know.

892
01:48:16.263 --> 01:48:18.899
It's no fun coming into work
with me on a Saturday.

893
01:48:19.033 --> 01:48:21.202
But I've had to do everything
by myself since...

894
01:48:22.470 --> 01:48:23.471
Well. you know. Mm-hm.

895
01:48:23.604 --> 01:48:25.139
I'll make it up to you tonight.

896
01:48:26.240 --> 01:48:28.309
How come you're keeping
all these urns

897
01:48:28.442 --> 01:48:30.111
for dead people?

898
01:48:30.244 --> 01:48:31.612
Uh...

899
01:48:31.746 --> 01:48:32.680
Well...

900
01:48:34.882 --> 01:48:36.417
It's sad. actually.

901
01:48:36.550 --> 01:48:39.153
These are the people whose
families never came for them.

902
01:48:39.286 --> 01:48:40.955
So. we keep them here
for a few months

903
01:48:41.088 --> 01:48:43.124
in case a family member
remembers

904
01:48:43.257 --> 01:48:44.592
to pick them up one day.

905
01:48:46.227 --> 01:48:47.928
Okay.
Don't touch anything. okay?

906
01:48:48.062 --> 01:48:49.430
That might be
about the cremator job.

907
01:48:49.563 --> 01:48:51.032
I'll be right back.

908
01:48:57.772 --> 01:48:59.807
"Christopher Leroy."

909
01:49:02.343 --> 01:49:04.311
"Ellie Bixler."

910
01:49:06.013 --> 01:49:08.549
Hey.

911
01:49:21.095 --> 01:49:22.963
Mom?

912
01:49:23.097 --> 01:49:24.999
Don't be scared. baby.

913
01:50:07.608 --> 01:50:09.276
Mommy's back.

913
01:50:10.305 --> 01:51:10.657
